name: MCBROWER TRIPPY STONEY
description: This avatar was created by Satoshi's Mom for @Jesse_McBrower – The avatar is based on a face swap of Jesse McBrower and the original T206 Honus Wagner baseball card, designed and issued by the American Tobacco Company from 1909-1911. The original avatar was created at the Baseball Hall of Fame in Cooperstown, NY in 2016 using an original copy of card.
